snippet.title: Diana Pretend Play Dress Up and New Make Up toys
snippet.description:
Diana Pretend Play Dress Up and does makeup with her new Make Up toys. The girl wants to be fashionable and beautiful. But, going out into the street, she meets girls in exactly the same outfits as hers! Diana changes clothes over and over again to be the most fashionable and not like other girls. New video for kids
